  },
  {
    title: "4. Cookies and Tracking",
    icon: "üç™",
    content: [
      "**Essential Cookies:** We use minimal essential cookies to ensure the website functions properly.",
      "**Analytics Cookies:** We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website. These cookies collect information in an anonymous form.",
      "**No Marketing Cookies:** We do not use cookies for remarketing or targeted advertising.",
      "**Your Control:** You can control and/or delete cookies as you wish. You can delete all cookies that are already on your computer and set most browsers to prevent them from being placed.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "5. Third-Party Services",
    icon: "üîó",
    content: [
      "We use a limited number of third-party services:",
